| **5. S3 Glacier Instant Retrieval**                        | Very low-cost storage for data thatâ€™s **rarely accessed** but needs **instant retrieval**. | For **archives or backups** you may occasionally need.                             | ğŸ’² (cheap storage, small retrieval cost)       |
